                                                    Antero Midstream GP raises $875 million in U.S. IPO
                                                


                                                    Reuters ‚Äì 
                                                    9:03 PM ET 05/03/2017
                                                


Antero Midstream GP LP, a partial owner of Antero Resources Corp's (AR) pipeline business, said on Wednesday it raised $875 million in an initial public offering . Antero is the largest midstream IPO of the last two years, as oil price volatility and pushback against new pipeline projects have driven down listing activity.

















